---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import teamImage from '@/assets/images/K3A0522-1-scaled-e1752455696919.jpg';
---

<section class="intro section">
  <div class="container-wide">
    <div class="intro-grid">
      <div class="intro-image">
        <Image src={teamImage} alt="Edwards & Smith Team" loading="lazy" width={744} height={744} />
      </div>
      <div class="intro-content">
        <h2>YOUR GO TO BUYERS AGENTS IN GOLD COAST, BRISBANE & BALI</h2>
        <p>
          Edwards & Smith Buyers Agents, founded by former AFL players Jake Edwards (Carlton) and Ely Smith (Brisbane Lions), is a trusted Queensland-based agency. Both players invested in property during their AFL careers to secure their futures. Ely, after working with Jake to buy an investment property, became fascinated with the role of a buyers agent and joined Jake in the business. They've since helped numerous AFL players, including Zach Bailey, Ben King, and Conor Budarick, find their dream homes. Their mission is to bridge the gap between buyers and the property market, offering transparent, authentic guidance for purchasing homes and investment properties. Their approach combines dual expertise and personalised support throughout the property journey.
        </p>
        <a href="/team" class="button-primary">MEET THE TEAM</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .intro {
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  .intro-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .intro-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .intro-content h2 {
    font-size: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .intro-content p {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6em;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .intro-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .intro-content h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .intro-content h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .intro-content p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
